{
  "texts": [
    "Performance Analysis and Trade-offs ASR vs. Clean Accuracy Trade-off: Our method achieves the lowest ASR (5.52%) among compared approaches, demonstrating effective backdoor removal.",
    "However, the clean accuracy (82.06%) is lower than NAD's 90% on ResNet-18.",
    "This gap stems from two factors:(1) Architectural Difference: Our custom CNN (∼623K parameters) is significantly smaller than ResNet-18 (∼11M parameters).",
    "The baseline clean accuracy before attack is already lower.",
    "(2) Unlearning Impact: The 0.43% accuracy drop during unlearning is actually smaller than most methods, retaining 99.48% of original performance.XAI Advantage: Unlike NAD and other black-box methods, our approach provides interpretable visual feedback."
  ]
}